## Build System

The `Makefile` wraps Nix commands for convenience:

- `make build`: Builds `.#docker-prod` and loads it into Docker.
- `make build-debug`: Builds `.#docker-debug` and loads it into Docker.
- `make up`: Runs `docker-compose up`.

